window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Conventional science has long held the position that 'the mind' is merely an illusion, a side effect of electrochemical activity in the physical brain. Now in paperback, Dr Jeffrey Schwartz and Sharon Begley's groundbreaking work, <i>The Mind and the Brain</i>, argues exactly the opposite: that the mind has a life of its own.</p>"; 
